{"tid":1211959,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【學術討論】如何智取+致各種原因唔衝既大家","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T02:03:09.000Z","uid":176985,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a1086bce49cbe2007c70c70ac07aa7f3d66265c5","tid":1211959,"uid":176985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:59:29.000Z","msg":"話說今日同人傾起如何智取<br />\n今日聽到個好似幾好又唔怕犯法既想法：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然二讀三讀係立法會表決<br />\n咁立法會議員取向都非常重要<br />\n不如大家直接向議員表達自己訴告<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例如打去事務處再三表達自己意願</span><br />\n如果議員同閣下意見相反<br />\n就可以講而家議員不代表我<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">相信香港至少有100萬選民都唔會選佢</span></span><br />\n相反如果議員既意向相同，咪即係有100萬選民支持佢囉！係咪good idea先<br />\n等佢地思考下需唔需要聽下<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">選民訴求</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我相信和平表達自己意願俾香港既立法會議員係非常重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且應該清晰而<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重複強調</span></span>，令佢地清楚d聽到我地選民既聲音<br />\n至於要<span style=\"color: red;\">打幾多次電話/send email/直接去事務處邊樣好</span>，我地就無討論到<br />\n強烈建議大家用堅定而無威脅/恐嚇/粗口成分既語氣同句子表達立場<br />\n無謂俾人有位入，告恐嚇<br />\n我地只係表達選民立場，等議員了解下民意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到好多各種原因唔衝既人士想爭取<br />\n想問下大家呢個方法點睇？<br />\n利申只係希望多一個方法爭取，畢竟多一個方法就多一分力，而且打電話相對容易實行<br />\n眼見好多人怨自己真係出唔到去<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/members/yr16-20/mem_cd.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Fmembers%2Fyr16-20%2Fmem_cd.pdf&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv8ZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=11a9a216\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/members/yr16-20/mem_cd.pdf</a><br />\n&uarr;可以check返自己個區既立法會議員聯絡方式&uarr;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有犯法既地方請告知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n注意返係意見既學術交流<br />\n請多多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a93581b6e60c0bcb9d9925782a60b771207b65","tid":1211959,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:01:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0667f8c35b8cc69bc1667aa180ef17fe3f8817f4","tid":1211959,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:03:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>g持</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3dfe75a3427cec7641f253c3011ebe224a675d3b","tid":1211959,"uid":176985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb129d3ec8f4a391377321fe1502f8cd24243d67","tid":1211959,"uid":176985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:35:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"52beaad682b03a897ca7f0067af513123a3d56ff","tid":1211959,"uid":255510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:38:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1d0a7e927b5bd6884800befdbdbc6f626c5c1a8d","tid":1211959,"uid":176985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:58:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e6366a181968f9224e5c8b42aff4abaf6097bdfa","tid":1211959,"uid":176985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:23:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"84342575c64eab557427a290a7f9165638a3866e","tid":1211959,"uid":176985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:48:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0d52723695fd00431da073ac2235be924d082edd","tid":1211959,"uid":176985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:00:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d24ffa93a1cf4a8dc531d33f58630d38947c1a68","tid":1211959,"uid":255510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n其實幾有用"},{"pid":"40cae845330ec0a48f4511d715b5ff4476109e14","tid":1211959,"uid":176985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"977bfdb0dadc50